title: Techni Mobili Modern Office Hutch Writing Desk, Grey
description: Create a beautiful workspace that will keep you motivated and focused throughout the day with our Techni Mobili Modern Desk with Hutch. Its spacious tabletop surface provides you with ample amount of room for all your must-have desk essentials – from your laptop, to notepads, stapler, cup holder and of course even your coffee mug.  This desk features clean lines and with a solid grey finish surface. It also includes an organizer hutch that features 2 large top shelves , two bottom convenient storage spaces as well as a storage drawer for easy access to your miscellaneous office supplies.
